'''[[soccer]] [[mom]]'''
#(''US'') a [[woman]] with [[school]]-[[age]] [[children]], especially one who spends time [[transport]]ing them between [[sporting]] [[activities]]. The term in its larger social context  can refer to a [[woman]] who is over ambitious with her childrens' success, often demonstrated by enrolling them in many different sporting activities.